{"word":"προσαπόλλυμι","slug":"προσαπόλλυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσαπόλλυμι</b></el> <el>(and <el>-ύω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ολέσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to destroy besides</i> or <i>also</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> aor2 <el>-ωλόμην</el>: <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-όλωλα</el>:— <i>to perish besides</i> or <i>with others</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to lose besides</i>, <el>τὴν ἀρχήν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}